"0,91 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"huile sur toile","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Histoire\r\nCollection particuli\u00e8re, \u00c9tats-Unis, 1956 ; Paris, coll. particuli\u00e8re ; acquis par l\u2019interm\u00e9diaire de Christie\u2019s en 1999.\r\n\r\nCommentaire\r\nPortrait d\u2019une belle facture qui \u00e9voque aussi bien Vouet que certains portraitistes hollandais comme Bartholomeus van der Helst (1613-1670). Il a \u00e9t\u00e9 rapproch\u00e9 par Charles Sterling en 1965 de la R\u00e9union d\u2019amis du Louvre (voir INV. 8063). Il demeure cependant singulier dans l\u2019oeuvre de Le Sueur, de sorte que nous pr\u00e9f\u00e9rons conserver avec prudence la mention \u00ab attribu\u00e9 \u00e0 \u00bb. Le tableau a \u00e9t\u00e9 peint sur une toile comprenant 10 \u00d7 11 fils au cm2. Il a \u00e9t\u00e9 restaur\u00e9 en couche picturale par\r\nMarie-Alice Belcour en 2004.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1999","startYear":1999,"endYear":1999}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Peintures","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Milovanovic, Nicolas, Peintures fran\u00e7aises du XVIIe du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Louvre \u00e9ditions \/ Gallimard, 2021","bibliographyDate":"2021","bibliographyDetail":"p. 155, ill.coul., n\u00b0334","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Cuzin, Jean-Pierre ; Allard, S\u00e9bastien (dir.), Mus\u00e9e du Louvre. Nouvelles acquisitions du d\u00e9partement des Peintures. 1996-2001, Paris, R.M.N., 2002","bibliographyDate":"2002","bibliographyDetail":"p. 107-108, ill. n\u0026b","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"M\u00e9rot, Alain, Eustache Le Sueur (1616-1655), Paris, Arthena, 1987","bibliographyDate":"1987","bibliographyDetail":"p. 175, Fig. 23 (n\u0026b), n\u00b0 24","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Sterling, Charles, \u00ab Eustache Le Sueur peintre de portraits \u00bb, dans Walter Friedl\u00e4nder zum 90. Geburtstag. Eine Festgabe seiner europa\u00efschen Sch\u00fcler, Freunde und Vereher, Berlin, 1965, p. 181-184","bibliographyDate":"1965","bibliographyDetail":"p. 181-184, ill. 3 pl. 40","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[{"value":"Eustache Le Sueur, Grenoble (France), Mus\u00e9e de Grenoble, 19\/03\/2000 - 02\/07\/2000 "}],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000067151\/0000571548_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000067151\/0000571548_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2016 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Tony Querrec","type":"face, recto, avers, avant ; vue d\u0027ensemble ; vue sans cadre","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000067151\/0000355319_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000067151\/0000355319_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2005 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ G\u00e9rard Blot","type":"face, recto, avers, avant ; vue d\u0027ensemble ; vue sans cadre","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000067151\/0000055203_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000067151\/0000055203_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2004 Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Dist. GrandPalaisRmn \/ Ang\u00e8le Dequier","type":"face, recto, avers, avant ; vue d\u0027ensemble ; vue sans cadre","position":2},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000067151\/0000055204_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/